The paper deals with convergence analysis of gradient descent applied to logistic regression, which is a common machine learning algorithm. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the convergence of parameters, which suggests that it may belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with optimization and convergence rates, which are topics commonly found in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
